### **MySQL Commands Basics**

|Command|Description|
|---|---|
|`mysql -u <user> -p<password> -h <IP>`|Connect to a MySQL server (no space after `-p`).|
|`show databases;`|List all databases.|
|`use <database>;`|Switch to a specific database.|
|`show tables;`|List all tables in the selected database.|
|`show columns from <table>;`|List columns in a table.|
|`select * from <table>;`|View all rows in a table.|
|`select * from <table> where <column> = "<value>";`|Filter rows based on a condition.|

