### **Dangerous / Security-Relevant Settings**

|Setting|Effect / Risk|
|---|---|
|`user`|OS user MySQL runs as.|
|`password`|Stored in plaintext in config; leakage = full DB access.|
|`admin_address`|IP for admin connections; misconfigured = remote exposure.|
|`debug`|Verbose output; can reveal sensitive info.|
|`sql_warnings`|Shows warnings on single-row inserts; can leak hints for attacks.|
|`secure_file_priv`|Limits file import/export; misconfiguration can allow file exfiltration.|

